{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/notification-system/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7cec5d04-c9e8-578d-9c23-322217f99087","html":"<p>在社交网络中，用户之间的通信方式主要分为两类，一类是直接进行交流（评论，私信），另一类则是与资源互动（点赞）并通知相关的用户（消息），今天我们来聊聊消息系统。</p>\n<h2 id=\"定义\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>消息系统是一种将社交网络中产生的消息推送给相关用户的系统，在这里我们可以得知，消息系统首先会记录消息，将它处理成文本形式，进而推送给用户。那么我们可以得到以下抽象</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Push Message -> User</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>我们将消息系统视为一个推送器，将用户需要知道的消息推送给它，但是这个过程中有许多细节需要考虑，比如如何得到这个消息，消息应该处理成什么形式，如何“推送”，用户自己来索取还是系统主动推给他，这些我们将在下文一一讨论。</p>\n<!--more-->\n<h2 id=\"消息\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF\" aria-label=\"消息 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>消息</h2>\n<h3 id=\"消息的格式\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"消息的格式 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>消息的格式</h3>\n<p>这一节，我们来定义消息的格式，先举两个消息的例子</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>小明赞同了你的回答xxxxxx</p>\n<p>小李在收藏夹xxx中添加了yyy</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>例子中包含消息的产生者（小明，小李），消息记录的行为（赞同，收藏），行为交互的对象（回答，收藏夹），行为操作的对象（yyy），我们将这些要素抽象为</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>产生者：Actor</p>\n<p>行为：Verb</p>\n<p>交互的对象： Target</p>\n<p>操作的对象：Object</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>如此，我们得到了消息类型的骨架，以python为例</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">actor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">verb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>有了这些基本的元素，我们还需要将它们构成一个字符串，我称之为模版</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>现在我们再来回顾之前的两个例子</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>小明点赞了你的回答xxxxx</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<p>这里actor为小明，verb为点赞，target为回答，点赞行为没有object，那么模版就是</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>actor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>verb<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">你的回答</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 使用了python的字符串内插语法</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"消息的获取\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96\" aria-label=\"消息的获取 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>消息的获取</h3>\n<p>通过上一小节，我们得到了消息的骨架，填充这个骨架需要从系统的上下文里获取数据。依然以点赞为例，当小明点赞你的回答时，系统应当产生一个事件，这个事件传递生成消息所必要的信息（AVOT），然后在队列中处理这个事件，将信息传递给Message类，进而得到结构化的消息</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> actor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> target_data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> object_data<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token boolean\">None</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>actor <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> actor\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target_data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> target_data\n        self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>object_data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> object_data\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">actor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>actor\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">verb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">pass</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 待重载</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 从target_data中得到target</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 从object_data中得到object</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 待重载</span>\n    \t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>actor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>verb<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">你的回答</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token comment\"># 使用了python的字符串内插语法</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>上面这段例子，我在注释里提到了待重载，因为我们可能有很多种具体的消息类型，比如点赞，收藏，关注，评论，回复等等，这些类型在结构上很相似，因此我们可以定义一个抽象的消息类，以及一些它的子类</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UpMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">verb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"点赞了\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FollowMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">verb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"关注了\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">StarMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Message<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">verb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"收藏了\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>同样的，系统中用户可以有多个点赞对象，所以 UpMessage 还可以进一步细化</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AnswerUpMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>UpMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>actor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>verb<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">你的回答</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CommentUpMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>UpMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f\"</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>actor<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>verb<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">你的评论</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">\"</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"消息的推送\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81\" aria-label=\"消息的推送 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>消息的推送</h3>\n<p>我们需要在得到消息的模版后将它推送给相应的用户，这一步有推和拉两种方式，推比较简单，当触发消息事件时，把消息存储到每个关注者的空间下。拉则相反，用户主动去问询他相关的资源是否有新消息产生并汇总。两种方式各有利弊，推的弊端在于如果某个资源的关注用户非常庞大，那么一次推的成本便很大，同样拉的弊端则相反，如果有某个用户关注了全部的资源，那么每次他去获取消息时拉的成本便很夸张。这里我来说说推的思路。</p>\n<p>我们需要给第二节的骨架添加一个新的属性</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">receiver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>followers</code></pre></div>\n<p>同时还需要将消息推到接收者的队列中，这里可以使用redis来存储消息</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">send</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># redis处理</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>我没有给出更具体的代码，但是我相信你可以在稍加尝试后自己实现出来。</p>\n<h2 id=\"扩展性\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E6%80%A7\" aria-label=\"扩展性 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>扩展性</h2>\n<p>上文我给出了一个消息系统的基本骨架，我们可以对它稍加扩展以便推送给用户的微信，邮箱，比如回复类的消息需要通过微信通知用户，那么我们只需要在 CommentMessage 类中实现微信相关的处理代码，就能立即得到微信的消息通知功能。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WechatMixin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">wechat_template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 根据微信公众号的设置填充模版</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">send_wechat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 发送给微信用户</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>实现出这样一个 mixin，我们就可以给任意类型的消息添加微信通知，当然微信的通知需要你具备微信开发相关的知识，如果不熟悉可以忽略。</p>\n<h2 id=\"后记\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%8E%E8%AE%B0\" aria-label=\"后记 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>后记</h2>\n<p>我在为上家公司工作时与 @wwj 设计并实现了消息系统，时间仓促，可能有一些不足的地方，本文以 python 为例并且仅揭示了当时设计的基本要素以及概要性的实现，如果你对此有什么问题，欢迎来信指教。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/notification-system/","tagSlugs":["/tag/web开发/","/tag/设计/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-05-30T22:40:32.169Z","description":"在社交网络中，用户之间的通信方式主要分为两类，一类是直接进行交流（评论，私信），另一类则是与资源互动（点赞）并通知相关的用户（消息），今天我们来聊聊消息系统。","tags":["Web开发","设计"],"title":"消息系统的概念、设计与实现","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/notification-system/"}}}